South Africa Plans First Five-Star Hotel in Kruger Park, Business Day Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-08T05:14:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-08/south-africa-plans-first-five-star-hotel-in-kruger-park-business-day-says.html
South Africa ’s government has
endorsed plans for the construction of the first five-star rated
hotel in the country’s Kruger National Park, Business Day
reported, citing Deputy Environmental Affairs and Tourism
Minister Rejoice Mabudafhasi.  The hotel must be constructed using the “latest green
technology,” the Johannesburg-based newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  